</nav>

<div class="background-overlay"></div>

<div class="container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="min-height: 80vh; padding: 0 2rem;">
  <div class="text-dark" style="width: 100%; max-width: none; padding: 1rem;">
    <div class="intro-banner mt-5">
      <h1 class="fw-bold display-4" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Ready to GeoDive?</h1>
      
      <p class="lead mb-3">
        Welcome to our country information portal! This website uses the REST Countries public API — a reliable and comprehensive source of country data — to bring you detailed and accurate information about countries worldwide.
      </p>
      <p class="lead mb-3">
        From basic facts like country names, capitals, and official languages to more in-depth details such as population, currencies, time zones, and regional blocs, this platform fetches live data directly from the API to keep you informed and up to date.
      </p>
      <p class="lead mb-3">
        Whether you're a student, traveler, researcher, or simply curious about the world, our website makes it easy to search for countries by name, capital city, or language. The results display a rich overview of each country's unique attributes, helping you discover and learn more about the diversity of nations across the globe.
      </p>
      <p class="lead mb-3">
        <strong>Important Note:</strong> This website only displays information that is available through the REST Countries public API. Some regions or territories commonly thought of as countries—such as England—may not have data available in the API. In such cases, the website will show a "No results found" message because the API itself does not include that data. This is a limitation of the data source and applies to all websites using this API.
      </p>
      <p class="lead">
        We aim to provide a user-friendly experience with a clean interface and intuitive search functionality, making country exploration fast and enjoyable. Thanks for visiting, and we hope you find this resource useful and inspiring!
      </p>
      
